  "body": "### Why?\r\nOur current practice for verifying that the user has copied the correct mnemonic includes re-typing the mnemonic in its entirety. This leaves users open to keyloggers that may copy the mnemonic, and is more time intensive than alternative verification methods.\r\n\r\nA common practice for verifying mnemonic (e.g. Decred, MyMonero) includes a drag and drop (gif below). A redesign of our verification and switching to a drag and drop approach will benefit users by making verification simpler and more secure.\r\n\r\n\r\n- [ ] Drag and drop word phrases in order instead of re-typing.\r\n\r\n\r\n",
